column10:
+Game is REALLY fun
+Have awesome learning tools;
+Online play works pretty well;
+Graphics are BEAUTIFUL (with proper and HDR support on W11);
+Character customization is cool, you have plenty of options, your char will look as you wand without you spending a single penny :)
+Good amount of single player modes;
+NO EXTRA PAID BULLSHIT

-I hate the main menu music :(
-Learning curve can intimidate new comers. I'm still probably way below average, but I feel every day I learn something;
-I use my 42" TV in ultra wide mode, and although the game do support ultra wide (which is AWESOME), its not working properly for me, it stretches the image and I can't use windowed full screen, for some unknown reason...

I'm loving it, 10/10 so far.
